Description
&#039;Journey South&#039; is the eponymous debut album from the 2005 X-Factor finalists. A collection of cover versions that are sure to appeal to fans of the original tracks as well as the legions of admirers they amassed with their sterling television performances. Includes the tracks &#039;One&#039; and &#039;English Rose&#039;.
